OL,3,CTwo arrested over death of 'Lip King'
OL,4,CJordan James Parke
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested over the
OL,7,Fdeath of the self-titled "Lip King"
OL,8,FJordan James Parke.
OL,10,FPolice confirmed on Monday that a 43-
OL,11,Fyear-old man and a 52-year-old woman
OL,12,Fwere arrested on Friday, February 20
OL,13,Fon suspicion of manslaughter.
OL,15,FThe pair have been bailed pending
OL,16,Ffurther investigation.
OL,18,FThe Metropolitan Police also told ITV
OL,19,FNews that Parke may have been
OL,20,Fundergoing a cosmetic procedure before
OL,21,Fhe died.
