OL,3,CTwo arrested over death of 'Lip King'
OL,4,CJordan James Parke
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police released the
OL,7,Ffollowing statement: "On Wednesday, 18
OL,8,FFebruary at 12:38hrs police were
OL,9,Fcalled by the London Ambulance Service
OL,10,Fto reports of an unconscious man on
OL,11,FLincoln Plaza, Canary Wharf.
OL,13,F"Officers attended alongside
OL,14,Fparamedics and a 34-year-old man was
OL,15,Fsadly declared dead at the scene. His
OL,16,Fnext of kin have been informed.
OL,26,@oD@VOUuD@AOU
