CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771938194
OL,3,CTwo arrested over death of 'Lip King'
OL,4,CJordan James Parke
OL,6,F"After police conducted urgent
OL,7,Fenquiries, a 43-year-old man and a 52-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman were arrested on
OL,9,FFriday, 20 February, on suspicion of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter. They have since been
OL,11,Fbailed pending further investigation.
OL,13,F"His death is currently being treated
OL,14,Fas unexplained, and an investigation
OL,15,Fto establish the full circumstances is
OL,16,Fongoing. However, officers are
OL,17,Freviewing information that suggests
OL,18,Fthe victim may have been undergoing a
OL,19,Fcosmetic procedure prior to his death.
OL,20,FThis is an initial line of enquiry at
OL,21,Fthis stage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
